  <div class="row">
    <div class="col about">
      <h1>MirrorTravis</h1>
      <div>
        <p>Hello, my name is Travis Stephens. I am a senior ruby on rails developer commited to making a fantastic product and supporting my clients in everything they do. I have been
        a professional rails developer for over three years and I take a lot of pride in my work and what I do. In addition to rails, I have a plethora of experience in creating end products
        for users and doing so in a resourceful manner. I believe that I am capable of fulfilling all your business needs and more.
